
@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:3001
@assist = 1111
@admin = admin-1234

### Salud
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### Listar productos (asistente)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?q=cloro
x-assist-code: {{assist}}

### Crear producto (asistente)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
x-assist-code: {{assist}}

{
  "name": "Bolsas de basura 95L",
  "brand": "Genérico",
  "presentation": "10 unid",
  "unit": "paquete",
  "category": "Cocina"
}

### Crear solicitud (asistente)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/requests
Content-Type: application/json
x-assist-code: {{assist}}

{
  "requester": "María",
  "items": [
    { "productId": 1, "quantity": 2, "unit": "botella", "notes": "Lavanda" },
    { "name": "Guantes de limpieza talla M", "quantity": 1, "unit": "par" }
  ]
}

### Listar solicitudes (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/requests
x-admin-code: {{admin}}

### Descargar JSON (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/requests/export
x-admin-code: {{admin}}
